de.hsbremen.tc.tnc.message.t.message

Interface TransportMessageHeader

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Data, TransportData
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    PtTlsMessageHeader

    public interface TransportMessageHeader
extends TransportData
    Generic transport message header base consisting of general parameters, that describe the message.

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      long getIdentifier()
      Returns an identifier for the message.
      long getLength()
      Returns the message length.

    • Method Detail

      • getIdentifier

        long getIdentifier()
        Returns an identifier for the message. The identifier is unique for a connection but does need to be globally unique. It must be a monotonically increasing counter staring with zero.
        Returns:
        the message identifier

      • getLength

        long getLength()
        Returns the message length. This is not standardized but needed for message processing.
        Returns:
        the message length
